{
  "id": "6a158541a823aa64fb29067c",
  "title": "客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結",
  "created": 1779795274,
  "updated": 1779795308,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a158541a823aa64fb29067c",
      "text": "客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795274,
      "updated": 1779795274
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158540000000000017de26",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeのログから自動抽出された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795274,
      "updated": 1779795307
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158561000000000017de57",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795307,
      "updated": 1779795307
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2a",
      "text": "[人狼ゲームの構造的衰退] をメタ化したフレームワーク。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2b",
      "text": "ゲームだけでなく[* 組織・政治議論・宗教コミュニティ]にも同型構造が見つかる。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2d",
      "text": "[*** 3つの前提条件]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2e",
      "text": "1. [* 客観的情報の供給が極端に乏しい] — 「事実」がほぼなく自己申告ベース",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de2f",
      "text": "2. [* 勝敗の判定が長期間ペンディング] — 個々の正しさは終局まで検証不能",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de30",
      "text": "3. [* 集団意思決定で進行] — 投票等の集団行動で次状態が決まる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de31",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de32",
      "text": "この3つが揃うと「正解が事後にしか分からないのに、その場で集団として何かを決めなければならない」状況が発生。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de34",
      "text": "[*** 5つの必然帰結 (A→E)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de35",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de36",
      "text": "[** A. 経験則 (=定石) が権威化する]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de37",
      "text": "正解判定が事後なので、過去にうまくいった型が代理指標に。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de38",
      "text": "やがて型は「最適解」ではなく「規範」になる。守らない奴は無能・戦犯。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3a",
      "text": "[** B. メタ言語が肥大化する]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3b",
      "text": "専門用語 ([ジャーゴンはIFFとして機能する]) が生まれ、副作用として",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3c",
      "text": "[* 用語共有が帰属意識の試験紙]になる。知らない人は仲間ではない。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3e",
      "text": "[** C. 議論対象が「事実」から「態度」にズレる]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de3f",
      "text": "観測可能事実が乏しい → 発言量や態度メタが論点に。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de40",
      "text": "本来の中身でなく、振る舞いそのものが評価対象になる。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de42",
      "text": "[** D. 新規参入者が二重に排除される]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de43",
      "text": "定石未習得 → 即座に弱者認定 → 弱者であること自体が集団の負債。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de44",
      "text": "「初心者お断り」が合理的選択になる。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de46",
      "text": "[** E. コミュニティが純化し縮小する]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de47",
      "text": "A-Dの結果、定石+メタ言語+お作法を守れる人だけ残る。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de48",
      "text": "新陳代謝停止、内輪化、外から見て気持ち悪い集団に。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4a",
      "text": "[*** 同型構造の例]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4b",
      "text": "\t対戦格闘ゲーム (フレーム単位の知識と立ち回り定石)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4c",
      "text": "\tTRPG/マダミスの一部コミュニティ",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4d",
      "text": "\t組織の戦略会議",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4e",
      "text": "\t政治的議論",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de4f",
      "text": "\t宗教コミュニティ",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de50",
      "text": "\t(拡張: 学術界、教養文化 → [教養とリベラルアーツのIFF性])",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de52",
      "text": "[*** 含意]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de53",
      "text": "\tこのパターンが見える集団は内輪化警報",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de54",
      "text": "\t設計で防ぐには [* 客観情報を増やす機構] が必要",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de55",
      "text": "\t\t[後発人狼系の構造的回避策] が具体例 (Among Us のタスク+ボディ発見)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a158549000000000017de56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795284,
      "updated": 1779795284
    }
  ]
}